about: Stackswap is a permissionless DEX and token project launchpad built on Bitcoin via the Stacks network. Stackswap is both an automated market maker (AMM) and an incubator for project looking to create their tokenized projects. With Stackswap's Token Launchpad, entrepreneurs and projects of any stage can launch their token supply on the Stacks blockchain. Investors of projects of any stage can also find projects that interest them and help support the entrepreneurs of these projects with funding, advice, and connections. Powered by years of research in artificial intelligence, Stackswap also plans to offer market forecasts and governance capabilities to users of its platform. What does permissionless mean? Permissionless means there is no central source or body that decides what the user can do on the platform. Whether you would like to create a pool, buy a token, or start a governance topic, you set your own rules.
